STATE of North Carolina
v.
Wayne Thomas JOHNSON. No. 119P00-14. Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 16, 2006. Wayne Thomas Johnson, Pro Se. Robert Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, Robert F. Johnson, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by defendant on the 6th day of November 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Alamance County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 16th day of November 2006."
